name: Release 4.1.0!
body:
No new features, just a lot of refactoring and fixing:
- Fixed display issues
- Updated Libraries
- Updated settings 
- Fixed crash related issues
- Major code refactoring
- Better permission handling
- Better translations

name: Release 4.0.6!
body:
Complete overhaul of entire app!!! (Waaay too much to list)

**Note:** I have started to use the beta channel on the Play store for those who are interested

name: Release 3.6.1!
body:
This is a big one...
- Optional default whitelist
- Dedicated whitelist menu
- Enhanced cleaning
- Switched to way newer libraries
- Auto whitelisting option
- Better looking settings menu (will improve further)
- Better looking clean menu

Next update will be feature SD card cleaning, and a file browser for adding to the whitelist.

name: Release 3.2.1!
body:
Minor update, just until all my exams are finished!
- Toast now shows amount removed
- Lots of translations
- Back button fix
- refactoring of code

name: Release 3.1.0!
body:
- added "one click clean" option
- hopefully fixed crashes at startup
- removed typewriter view
- simplified filter options

name: Release 3.0.0!
body:
- added Chinese (traditional) support
- hopefully fixed most of the crashes
- added "aggressive filter"

name: Beta 3.0.0
body: This build features the new aggressive filter. In beta to see what android versions it works on
